<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4612540>
    dc:description "Fig. 11. Bopyroides hippolytes (Kröyer, 1838), reference female (CIEHI401001) (A–H): A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C. Left maxilliped, external view. D. Left side of barbula. E. Left oostegite 1, external view. F. Left oostegite 1, internal view. G. Left pereopod 1. H. Left pereopod 7. Reference male (CIEHI401002) (I–L): I. Dorsal view. J. Ventral view. K. Right antenna and antennule. L. Left pereopod 1. Scale: 1 mm (A, B); 0.5 mm (C, E–H,); 0.25 mm (D, I–L)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4612540/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

